    <article class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
      <div class="mb-8">
        <span class="text-sm text-gray-400">Guide - Updated April 2026</span>
        <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mt-1 mb-4">Best English Tutors for Business in 2026</h1>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-400">From executive coaching to meeting prep. These 7 platforms help working professionals master business English.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="bg-emerald-900/30 border border-emerald-700/50 rounded-xl p-6 mb-8">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-between flex-wrap gap-4">
