      </div>

      <p class="text-xs text-gray-400 mt-8"><em>Affiliate disclosure: We earn a commission when you sign up through links marked with an asterisk. This does not affect our editorial reviews. <a href="/affiliate-disclosure/" class="underline">See our full affiliate disclosure.</a></em></p>
    
